About
Our Story
Rookies is a family-owned business opened in 2011 by the Sessa-Beetz family. We pride ourselves in not only providing freshly made food to order and giving great service to our valued customers whether you’re dining in, taking food to go, or getting a party catered but also a priority in working with the needs within our community.
As we move into our 14th year of business, Rookies has focused on helping our community by holding Fundraising events, give back nights, sponsoring local youth and adult sports teams and organizations, supporting local nonprofits, working with our first responders, local schools, and government, supporting other local small businesses, and many other areas in showing appreciation and thanks to our valued customers. Whether you’re new to the area or already a Rookies valued customer, we invite you to come in and enjoy some awesome food, a specialty cocktail or bring your dog and grab a table for food and drinks in our pet friendly patio area! We accommodate from small to large parties inside or outside upon request.
Please contact us @
(352) 593-4114
for additional information on event planning inside or on our patio, birthdays, corporate events, and catering. We take reservations of 8 people or more.
Thank you in advance for choosing Rookies Family Grill & Bar
